title: When There Were No Starks in Winterfell (2019)
description:
From our recurring Saturday livestream: Sean and Aziz discuss and geek out over the Stark kids' arcs (Starcs?) around the end of Clash/start of Storm, which is the beginning of the point at which all the Starks have left Winterfell. Includes some book to show comparisons and predictions on how some of the Starcs will end. Published October 2, 2019.
